Package: motherduck
Type: Package
Title: Collection of Utilities to Manage a "Motherduck" Database
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Alejandro", "Hagan",
      email = "alejandro.hagan@outlook.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Collection of database utilities for "Motherduck" database
    This provides utilities and metadata function support to simplify the management, connection,
    uploading and management of a Motherduck database platform.
    This package requires an account www.motherduck.com to apply its functions.
